==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Leningrad
<hw>Leningrad</hw> <pos>prop. n.</pos> <def>A city in the European part
of Soviet Russia; the former capital of Russia. The name was formerly
<altname>St. Petersburg</altname> and <altname>Petrograd</altname>, and
was changed back to <altname>Saint Petersburg</altname> (<tran>Sankt
Peterburg</tran> in Russian) in 1992.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> St. Petersburg, Peterburg, Petrograd, Saint
Petersburg.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Leninism</ent>⟦br⟧
